cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for word sense disambiguation, which are typically covered in the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the use of a large corpus for training and evaluation may also fall under the sub-category of cybernetics (cs.CY).
